I figured out what was causing the weird /millchan not found page. If you don't select generate a certificate but instead select no certificate as your certificate for your postit goes through locally but never gets seeded to any peers. You have to press generate certificate, and do it again for every post, to have anonymity. Or atleast I would be correct if anyone sees this post.
It doesn't have to be so empty. I can't access millchan as of 01/10/2021 but still. Also happen to know if ben davidson is trustworthy and proof if otherwise?
